title: Gossip | Watch: Lena Dunham talks women's issues, believes in horoscopes and psychics
text:
The more we see of her, the more we love. Not only is she addressing women's issues on a public level, she's also penning a newsletter which you can get sent directly to your inbox (when you figure out the sign up process, it seems tricky), which focussing on political figures and your reproductive system.
The highlight of the below video is where she admits to believing in the works of psychics, which many would consider a point of ridicule - mostly those who've never been to a psychic. Try it, you will be amazed. I've been to LOADS. When you get a bad one, it's really bad, but when you get a good one - MIND. BLOWN.
